s/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T01:51:13.000Z","msg":"習近平 = 巨人入面既艾倫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T02:31:21.000Z","msg":"又真係似喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n開頭仲個個笑佢on9仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88d8e220927c2199866ab716c29c81f147aed4a8","tid":2000443,"uid":271807,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T02:33:14.000Z","msg":"今次真有見地"},{"pid":"19a88a037d721758dcbb0e44b247118e90a5e971","tid":2000443,"uid":14449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T03:38:18.000Z","msg":"Wan Chin<br />\n6 mins &middot; <br />\n陳雲：政治市，國師午間教路。保安局長說，將引用反恐法例，凍結示威者的家產。去年護法運動期間，有三百萬香港人上街的，全部可以控告。<br />\n政府曲線提醒各位，經濟衰退及治安動亂來了，要及早做好資產轉移海外、人員移民海外的準備。<br />\n（今早寫了個長貼文，不過因為內容涉及學術機密，故此在一個小時之後刪除。詳細討論，在閉門會議。）"},{"pid":"867ae5cd60ec9173ea99da501765d8defffc8d8c","tid":2000443,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T06:22:39.000Z","msg":"錯錯錯<br />\n要mc 全錯一樣<br />\n都係實力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"922a5da62fca34aebe0c86a1d20aef2cccbfd07d","tid":2000443,"uid":328232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6110763f03d5d733043fc4a9a527195da8782a0d","tid":2000443,"uid":306914,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T01:50:58.000Z","msg":"呢篇文算唔算係食咗藥先寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T06:30:49.000Z","msg":"算，但佢個論點好多人都已經提過，sup9才子陶傑就係其中一個例子"}]}